17:10.366 --> 17:15.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: He's worked 25
years as both as a top federal
a prosecutor and as defense

17:16.766 --> 17:17.766 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
attorney.

17:17.766 --> 17:19.866 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

17:19.866 --> 17:21.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLES GRASSLEY (R), Iowa: Do
you affirm that the testimony
you're about to give before

17:21.866 --> 17:26.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the committee will be the truth,
the whole truth and nothing
but the truth, so help you,

17:27.066 --> 17:28.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
God?

17:28.300 --> 17:30.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
CHRISTOPHER WRAY, FBI
