was asked about his allegiance.

18:06.700 --> 18:11.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHRISTOPHER WRAY: My loyalty is
to the Constitution, to the rule
of law, and to the mission of

18:12.233 --> 18:14.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
the FBI.

18:14.300 --> 18:17.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And no one asked me for any
kind of loyalty oath at any
point during this process, and

18:17.600 --> 18:19.000 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
