18:19.000 --> 18:21.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
LISA DESJARDINS: And
about his conviction.

18:21.066 --> 18:25.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHRISTOPHER WRAY: I believe
to my core that there's only
one right way to do this job,

18:28.066 --> 18:32.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and that is with
strict independence,
by the book, playing it
straight, faithful to the

18:33.766 --> 18:35.833 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Constitution.

18:35.833 --> 18:39.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Wray spoke
about his 2004 pledge to leave
the Justice Department over

18:39.366 --> 18:44.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
