Donald Trump Jr. meeting?

40:01.300 --> 40:03.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KARINE JEAN-PIERRE,
Democratic Strategist: I
think it's pretty damaging.

40:03.866 --> 40:07.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We finally have evidence,
e-mails, that were not
fake news, because it
was actually delivered,

40:09.900 --> 40:13.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
released by Don Jr., that shows
that a foreign - - he met --
he and Paul Manafort and Jared

40:15.400 --> 40:20.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
