agent in the sole, sole purpose
of trying to get information

40:22.033 --> 40:25.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
given by a foreign
adversary, intelligence
from a foreign adversary.

40:25.533 --> 40:27.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And I think that's
pretty damaging.

40:27.533 --> 40:31.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
