you're as completely
as transparent as
you possibly can be.

41:21.900 --> 41:26.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Actually, the reason we know
this is because Jared Kushner
and Paul Manafort updated the

41:28.800 --> 41:31.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
