41:41.933 --> 41:44.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But the underlying facts still
prove absolutely no criminality.

41:44.600 --> 41:46.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Absolutely
no criminality?

41:46.700 --> 41:49.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
